info.author: Valentin Lorentz
classifiers: Topic :: Communications :: Chat :: Internet Relay Chat
Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description: A robust, full-featured Python IRC bot with a clean and flexible plugin API. Equipped with a complete ACL system for specifying user permissions with as much as per-command granularity. Batteries are included in the form of numerous plugins already written.
info.name: limnoria
info.summary: A modified version of Supybot (an IRC bot and framework)
